snippet.title: Embla - Dream of Redemption (Character Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
Embla's ever-growing powers have clouded her mind. She can no longer distinguish the boundary between dream and reality.
The dark world is slowly tainted by blood. Life and death are but a moment away.
Embla wanders in her endless dream, trying to find love and redemption.
